      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The exterior finish retains its original factory luster, free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings, appearing as deep and reflective as the day it left the showroom. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it carries only that distinct, clean scent of a high-end automobile. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is impeccable, with a comprehensive service history documented from day one. It drives tight, smooth, and powerful, offering a level of refinement that only a perfectly preserved example can provide. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
